      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个简单的问候场景序列图。有两个参与者：Alice 和 John。Alice 主动打招呼，John 回复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
