    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，两个参与者。那 Alice 发给 John 的消息内容是什么？还有，这条消息是同步调用还是异步的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John"
